Description: Quaternion manipulation package for Octave
DescDetail: <<
Package for the manipulation of Quaternions used for frame transformation.

This package provides the following additional functions:

Quaternions:
	quaternion
	qi
	qj
	qk
	q2rot
	rot2q
Quaternion Methods:
	@quaternion/abs
	@quaternion/blkdiag
	@quaternion/cat
	@quaternion/columns
	@quaternion/conj
	@quaternion/diag
	@quaternion/diff
	@quaternion/exp
	@quaternion/inv
	@quaternion/ispure
	@quaternion/log
	@quaternion/norm
	@quaternion/rows
	@quaternion/size
	@quaternion/size_equal
	@quaternion/unit
Overloaded Quaternion Operators:
	@quaternion/ctranspose
	@quaternion/eq
	@quaternion/horzcat
	@quaternion/ldivide
	@quaternion/minus
	@quaternion/mldivide
	@quaternion/mpower
	@quaternion/mrdivide
	@quaternion/mtimes
	@quaternion/plus
	@quaternion/power
	@quaternion/rdivide
	@quaternion/subsasgn
	@quaternion/subsref
	@quaternion/times
	@quaternion/transpose
	@quaternion/uminus
	@quaternion/uplus
	@quaternion/vertcat
<<

